            <title>[CASSANDRA-1613] index created from cli does not show up in keyspace metadata</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1613</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;create column family Category with comparator=UTF8Type and column_metadata=[&lt;/p&gt;
{column_name:level, validation_class:IntegerType, index_type:0, index_name:CategoryLevelIdx}
&lt;p&gt;]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;succeeds, but after this&lt;br/&gt;
&apos;show keyspaces&apos; does not reveal the presence of the index. Only the column family is shown.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
